        <h2>Physics-informed Neural Network for Leaf Trait Inversion</h2>
        <p>
          This project investigates how physical radiative transfer models such as
          PROSPECT-PRO can be combined with neural encoders for robust leaf trait
          inversion.
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li>Keywords: PROSPECT-PRO, PI-NN, VAE, Attention, Leaf Spectra</li>
          <li>Traits: Cab, Car, Cw, Prot, CBC</li>
          <li>Data: Reflectance / Transmittance spectra</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="project">
        <h2>YOLOv8 OBB / Segmentation on RK3588</h2>
        <p>
          This project builds an embedded real-time vision pipeline using YOLOv8,
          RKNN, ROS, and camera streaming on RK3588.
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li>Keywords: YOLOv8, RKNN, ROS, RK3588, Segmentation</li>
          <li>Tasks: Detection, mask extraction, angle estimation, offset publishing</li>
          <li>Platform: Linux, ROS Noetic, Rockchip NPU</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
